            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">4. A 49-year-old man presents with a history of difficulty sleeping. He reports feeling increasingly tired and general weakness which he attributes to his poor sleep pattern. Additionally, the patient has noticed he has gained weight and sweats very easily. On examination, the patient has coarse facial features. The most likely<br />\ndiagnosis is:</p>"
