            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">8. Polyuria<br />\nA 29-year-old man presents with a 4-week history of polyuria and extreme thirst.<br />\nThe patient denies difficulty voiding, hesitancy or haematuria, although the urine<br />\nis very dilute. The patient does not believe he has lost any weight and maintains a<br />\ngood diet. No findings are found on urine dipstick. The most appropriate<br />\ninvestigation is:</p>"
