            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">26. Diabetes management (2)<br />\nA 49-year-old man has recently been diagnosed with type 2 diabetes and is being<br />\ncarefully monitored. He has been advised to maintain a healthier diet and lifestyle,<br />\nhe attends a follow-up clinic and claims to have been following the diet stringently<br />\nsince his last appointment three months ago. The most appropriate investigation is:</p>"
